metadata.name: Synti Flight
metadata.description:
Sinti is a visualized AI interface, a digital being born on the border of the digital and material worlds, an ambassador of Ecofuturism values, a reality where technology and nature live in symbiosis. 
In the world of the future, humanity and AI are a single whole, complementary entities, creating and exploring the universe through the prism of technology and art. Digital clothes - is limitless self-expression in the world of Web 3.0, and Synti is a guide and companion of humanity in the digital universe, a universe without boundaries and limits of imagination and creativity.

2022
